Description:
Convert a date/time string to linear time.

Files:
doc/parse-datetime.texi
lib/parse-datetime.h
lib/parse-datetime.y
m4/tm_gmtoff.m4
m4/parse-datetime.m4

Depends-on:
bison
c99
c-ctype
stdbool
gettime
gettext-h
